{"tid":95070,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[呻吟][長文少圖]其實幾時先有返大家所認識嘅香港...","createTime":"2017-01-25T17:40:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T02:34:19.000Z","uid":13586,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1a3ae997d727ca85c0242dd2a78b9a4ded1e979d","tid":95070,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T17:40:17.000Z","msg":"回想返小弟初次參加示威已經係2012年嘅光復上水站，嗰時上水已經通街水貨客同蝗蟲，但嗰時其他地方仲食緊花生，甚至屌我地阻住人坐火車...<br />\n<br />\n究竟我地阻人D定班水貨客蝗蟲阻人D？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後係2013年三號風球下七一遊行，嘉年華左幾年仲可以咁多人，覺得香港仲有希望<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/35V733Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F35V733Y.jpg&h=94590739&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w8F6n7v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw8F6n7v.jpg&h=77a6019f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到HKTV發牌風波，大家都明咩事，WIKI日日燒錢燒到HKTV變左網上購物<br />\n嗰時同好多香港人仲以為有機會開放大氣電波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2eHD3Jb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2eHD3Jb.jpg&h=0692e18b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3x1d18k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3x1d18k.jpg&h=9226d2ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到2014年，咩立場都好都應該認同好重要嘅一年<br />\n由14年歷年最多嘅71，到九月雨傘前嘅學界示威，有份夜媽媽上到禮賓府，到928硬食幾粒催淚彈，好多人份工都冇埋都賭呢次一定可以改變到香港<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7627H5K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7627H5K.jpg&h=58468228&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hU8N965.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhU8N965.jpg&h=6c649e05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6R6d897.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6R6d897.jpg&h=02dba19f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9zeSX1R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9zeSX1R.jpg&h=05b25325&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者意志消磨，年尾清場；或者已在心中，遍地開花；或者燒到眼眉，2015年光復行動唔止上水，沙田元朗屯門亦都有，好開心好感動。反過來一句：上水人咁撚廢嫁！割左上水佢啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心諗：呢幾年做左d咩佢地可以咁自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再到2016年民憤早已上頂，一場魚蛋革命，間接令唔少本土勢力抬頭。新東補選同立會選舉終於有我想投嘅人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由示威，口講-&gt;到社運，行動-&gt;到參選，實踐 ...成個structure可以睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後一個一個被DQ，但已經冇人出聲，已經覺得出聲係冇用<br />\n到而家689收皮個個開香檳，但唔係民眾壓力逼到佢下台，只係夠任期而走<br />\n<br />\n之後品客大耍公關；淋病大談離地；孽瘤繼續恨做；胡官繼續抽水...<br />\n人地點教仔仲大單過自己冇票投，繼續1200人投一個被DQ嘅議員票數仲少嘅人...<br />\n<br />\n 再諗返，香港已經有好多個最，多到數唔哂：<br />\n全球最長工時<br />\n全球樓價最難負擔城市<br />\n全球最貴城市生活成本<br />\n.......<br />\n<br />\n有時食老麥食到好灰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/91042/page/1?ref=web\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/91042/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n樓主唔講，我都唔知自己原來都係一隻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人人做哂樓奴、窮忙族、政治冷感、港豬...<br />\n日日都聽到批鬥座、死蝗蟲、大陸柒事、犯罪集團休班警、細過車位嘅屋...<br />\n<br />\n可能講到1999<br />\n或者我仲細，過多兩個月先24歲<br />\n係咪人愈大，希望會變成奢望？<br />\n<br />\n其實香港人仲想港豬到幾時？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幾時先有返928時候嘅激動？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幾時先有返大家所認識嘅香港？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者我呢個大同世界嘅夢想仲難過買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c1d130754788645e18da6e311a142405ad45c6","tid":95070,"uid":74986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T17:43:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30efdbe76fb994f351b541d25db94fdd16f19b28","tid":95070,"uid":49424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T17:46:22.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16109dd5dac377ebd1c286f55fb67abf0e3baef4","tid":95070,"uid":54223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T17:51:04.000Z","msg":"你預左無改變好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nhk 人大部份都理左娛樂先"},{"pid":"a6a52145d0fd58380ff127e331b14c274d00cfe0","tid":95070,"uid":41701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T17:52:51.000Z","msg":"唔好講勇武，<br />\n有時激動少少鬧多兩句就會有人出黎話：洗唔洗咁激動呀？唔關你事嘅出少句聲啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71865ecfd75e4a854b2ee32e41af971eb8be0b9f","tid":95070,"uid":70415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T17:53:14.000Z","msg":"中共既目標就係令到香港人攰，等我地連一絲反抗既慾望都唔再有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到時佢就可以為所欲為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327cd9ee176a7ab0dc103e12bae2a9457c86153c","tid":95070,"uid":59700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T17:54:08.000Z","msg":"有得走好走"},{"pid":"bace6a6796be335539a6c7cffd80593667741e3d","tid":95070,"uid":70527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T17:54:33.000Z","msg":"never"},{"pid":"22d3d7a177fdd8ce74c2c720c9a29e577ea8996a","tid":95070,"uid":15236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T17:55:35.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f454f515047adaffbc2f0acf39922af770d145","tid":95070,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T02:22:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好講勇武，<br />\n有時激動少少鬧多兩句就會有人出黎話：洗唔洗咁激動呀？唔關你事嘅出少句聲啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個最冇癮<br />\n呢幾年身邊d fd 講得最多唔係我唔熟政治，xxx係邊個，係發生咩事<br />\n<br />\n而係唔好咁激動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每次都幫緊佢地爭取緊本應，係本應擁有嘅權利，但一一潑冷水<br />\n<br />\n可幸嘅，part time 同中學死黨仲有良知，有份幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9be2f3bf9401da92f2af5fe06838c0990c1a325d","tid":95070,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T02:34:19.000Z","msg":"已灰心<br />\n立法會選舉知道香港人要咩<br />\n本土派狗咬狗骨<br />\n亦都無勇氣再冒住前途風險幫香港人爭取乜<br />\n香港人最叻係fb講大愛做keyboard戰士<br />\n決定搵夠錢顧掂自己生活做港豬算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}